Last August, Rampage and AE's were broken due to a patch.  This made Emp of Ssra a much easier encounter.  Tindi was up for Blood, and our 4th shot at emp after blood.  The results of the discussion was that neither guild would touch blood/emp, and rumors were flying of emp b eing gm-killed on other servers.  Well, BoTS then moved up and took out blood/emp, saying that it was ok for them to kill the gimped out emp because they had done so in the past.<br>
<br>
Now, Gromm is attacking Tindi through the same mechanism, pride.  And I see no reason for someone to do something that is obviously the less intelligent choice simply because they are prideful.<br>
<br>
