Leet Strat #2: Argue constantly with your raid leaders into letting you melee Omnifiend. Success! Woah, he drops a lot faster when you melee! Argue constantly with your raid leaders into letting you melee Fennin Ro. OMFG I MELEED FENNIN AND DIDN'T GET HIT AT ALL! WOW!! OMFG I R TEH LEET SHIT DAWG!!! Damn those mobs are gimp. Who gives a fuck how they died? It took what, a day to learn pulling fire? A day to learn pulling water? Air might have taken a day or two longer without &quot;omfg leet outside knowledge&quot; (um, really, who gives a fuck, again?) You realize the Fennin Ro script is six fucking hours long? People would have to be RETARTED to be able to spawn it and not learn it in the same session.<br>
